title: Vikings sweep JV Classic titles
text:
Brandon Sun - PRINT EDITION Vikings sweep JV Classic titles 
Vincent Massey’s junior varsity volleyball teams won their own Viking Classic tournament on Saturday. 
The JV girls won the title with a close two-set victory over the Neelin Spartans. Massey beat Neelin 30-28, 25-21 to take the title. Neelin earned its spot in the final with a three-set victory over Crocus in the semifinal. 
In the boys’ event, the host Vikings topped the Spartans 2-1 (25-22, 16-25, 15-13) in the final. We want you to tell us what you think of our articles.
